name: Karate Sheep
overview: Trico is an enthusiastic sheep who loves to share new objects and ideas with the rest of the flock. This causes ruckus in the mountain pastures, which all inevitably end up at Wanda’s expense, a tough ewe whose job is to keep the sheep safe. Not a small feat, especially when Wolf is always lurking, waiting to make the most of this newfound chaos.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Two clever sheep use karate and high-tech gadgets to protect their flock from a hungry wolf who's determined to make them all his dinner.

episodes.name: Wanda's Apprentice
episodes.overview: Trico's gadgets keep distracting Wanda's apprentice; Wolf tricks Wanda into teaching him karate; Wanda plays soccer with the flock.

episodes.name: Top Dog!
episodes.overview: Trico's lawnmower makes Wanda jealous; Wanda performs feats of strength; Trico's disappearing magic tricks amaze Wanda.

episodes.name: Red Card for Wanda
episodes.overview: A mysterious object takes Wanda, Trico and Wolf on a wild ride; Trico's stench terrorizes the flock; Trico tries to teach Wanda how to read.

episodes.name: Robot Mower Rampage
episodes.overview: Wanda has trouble playing sidekick to Trico; Wanda doesn't like what she sees in the mirror; Trico and Wolf switch outfits.

episodes.name: Wonder Wanda
episodes.overview: Trico gets a new hairdo; the flock hires a sheepdog when Wanda gets injured; Wanda can't seem to follow the rules of the road.

episodes.name: Trico's Magic Show
episodes.overview: Trico's whoopee cushion doesn't amuse Wanda; Wanda, Trico and Wolf get lost in the woods; with Wolf away, Wanda learns to relax.

episodes.name: The Thingy
episodes.overview: Wanda and Trico run a footrace; Trico adopts a new pet; Trico gets jealous of Wanda's new gadget.

episodes.name: Smells Like Trouble
episodes.overview: Wanda and Trico struggle after a bad night of sleep; the flock experiments with different exercise styles; Wanda and Wolf battle with boulders.

episodes.name: Bad Teacher
episodes.overview: Wolf learns to attack from above; Trico's novelty fangs freak out Wanda; when Wanda hurts her back, only Trico's magic hands can help her.

episodes.name: Wannabe Hero
episodes.overview: Wanda and Trico keep Wolf safe while he sleepwalks; Trico and Wolf train for a boxing match; Trico protects Wanda from tickle attacks.

episodes.name: Mirror, Mirror Who's the Strongest?
episodes.overview: Wanda and Trico don't want to share the swing; Trico gives Wanda a present she doesn't appreciate; a fly gets on Trico's nerves.

episodes.name: Sheep in Wolf's Clothing
episodes.overview: Trico builds an outhouse for the flock; Wanda tries herding with a whistle; Wanda gets emotional over a romantic story.

episodes.name: Trico's Fake Hair
episodes.overview: Wanda learns how to let loose; Trico doesn't want to share his snack; Trico introduces Wanda to blowing bubbles.
